	(lib_symbols)
	(text "POWER  (reuse AES-DAC power tree)
Components:
 - J: barrel jack DCJ200-10-A  (9V in, center-negative) -> VIN
 - U: TPS7A4901  -> +5V analog
 - U: TPS7A4901  -> +3V3 digital
 - U: TPS7A4901 (opt) -> +3V3_CLK clean rail (CS2000+xtal)
 - U: APX803S05-29SA-7 supervisor -> RST_N
 - D: VBUS OR diode (USB_VBUS vs +5V)   [D8]
 - decoupling, ferrite beads per rail
Rails (+5V,+3V3,+3V3_CLK,GND) distributed via global power symbols.
Export RST_N as hierarchical label."
